incident_updates.body: As part of our continuous improvement plan, maintenance is scheduled on our network infrastructure. Start time : 17/12/2025 00:30 UTC End time : 17/12/2025 03:30 UTC Service impact : The private network (vRack) will be temporarily unavailable for approximately 30 minutes for the servers located in the racks listed below : G108A14 G108A15 G108A16 G108B01 G108B04 G108B05 G108B06 G108B10 G108B11 G108B19 G118B02 G118B03 G118B06 G118B09 G118B10 G118B12 G118B13 G118B14 G118B15 G118B16 Please note that the maintenance may take less time than expected. Service improvement : Following our continuous improvement policy, we will be doing a maintenance on multiple network equipment. Thank you for your understanding.
